Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:47.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創造すら忘れた　その座に光は当たんないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:49.87,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}希望語る　不満散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:51.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}革命の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:55.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}誰にも追いつけないところまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:01:02.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}突き抜け　修羅を越え　いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:07.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今にも圧倒的な支配が　僕の喉を乾かしたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.97,0:01:12.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奪わせないものは夢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:15.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}燃やせ　全神経の感覚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:19.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}誰に届けたいかすらもわからない音に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}意義は宿らない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:30.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:34.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}その頂へと
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.35,0:00:42.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}牢笼里多么的安全　舒适而没有压力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.41,0:00:47.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}忘却了创造　这里将被光明抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.50,0:00:49.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来倾吐希望　让不满爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.97,0:00:51.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}吹响革新的号角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:55.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我要全力攀登　再不让他人企及
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.42,0:01:02.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}突破血雨腥风　让他们全都辟易
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.41,0:01:07.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}绝对的控制　将令我咽喉干渴无法言语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.97,0:01:12.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}却无法夺去我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:15.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}让一切感官嘶吼激昂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:19.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不把炽热的情感寄托在音符中唱响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:25.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}怎会令心脏热血滚烫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.01,0:01:30.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我需要光　更多的光
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.78,0:01:34.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}向着顶点冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:37.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:39.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I'm proud of myself and you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.06,0:01:42.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We must be the change we wish to see
